      "description": "Hey there! You've got to see this beauty. Honestly, it\u2019s like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014I've babied this car since day one! It's in absolutely pristine condition, inside and out, and drives like a total dream. If you're looking for something that feels brand new without the brand-new price tag, this is the one. Come take it for a spin, you won't be disappointed!",
