      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional 2019 BMW M2 Competition in Hockenheim Silver Metallic. This vehicle is the definition of showroom quality, having been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage since day one. The exterior paint is flawless, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating that yields a deep, mirror-like finish with zero swirl marks or rock chips. Inside, the Black Dakota leather with blue stitching remains taut and pristine; the bolsters show no wear, and the cabin still retains that distinctive new-car aroma. Mechanically, the car is perfect. It has a full, documented service history exclusively through BMW certified technicians, with the crucial 1,200-mile break-in service performed precisely on schedule. Every button, switch, and feature functions exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. This is a pristine example for a discerning enthusiast who demands the absolute best. Includes two keys, all original manuals, and a custom-fitted car cover.",
      "price": 48500.0,
